(64, 1, '2011-12-12 18:38:13', '2011-12-12 18:38:13', 'We love to share our expertise! UCAS representatives frequently speak before seminars and conferences to provide government finance officers with up-to-date information and analysis of markets and share ideas on the importance of developing a structured approach to managing their public funds.  In this section you’ll find presentations and timely articles from past issues of Footnotes.\r\n\r\nIf you’d like to schedule a presentation tailored to your group – or if you don’t find the topic you’re looking for, please call us at (888-516-9594) and we’ll find the person or information you’re looking for.', 'Our Library', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'our-library', '', '', '2012-03-19 13:28:15', '2012-03-19 13:28:15', '', 7, 'http://cashadvisory.umbaugh.com/?page_id=64', 0, 'page', '', 0),
