(108, 2, '2012-03-07 13:51:10', '2012-03-07 13:51:10', 'Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Duis quis lectus nibh, et placerat tortor. Donec et diam vel tellus ultrices pharetra. Quisque iaculis lectus at ipsum ultrices dapibus. Ut erat diam, convallis ac imperdiet ac, egestas sit amet nulla. Nunc facilisis, lorem dapibus tincidunt volutpat, nulla arcu cursus dolor, ut pharetra quam enim nec quam. Suspendisse justo magna, pulvinar vel gravida eget, pretium pellentesque nibh. Nulla aliquet gravida diam sit amet iaculis. Proin vitae ligula tellus. Nulla commodo venenatis pellentesque. Nullam tincidunt, libero placerat lobortis pellentesque, justo diam euismod lectus, id mattis mi orci vitae lacus. Aliquam vitae nisi vel neque porttitor lacinia vel vitae elit. Morbi augue nulla, laoreet et fringilla quis, malesuada id ligula. Nam tempus auctor semper. Nulla eget ligula erat. Ut a orci turpis. Integer eu ligula erat.', 'Our Library', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '64-revision-4', '', '', '2012-03-07 13:51:10', '2012-03-07 13:51:10', '', 64, 'http://cashadvisory.umbaugh.com/64-revision-4', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(109, 1, '2012-03-06 15:52:53', '2012-03-06 15:52:53', 'At UCAS, we understand that municipalities continue to face budget challenges and are increasingly being asked to do more with less.  Developing an efficient banking and investment program that not only protects your funds, but also provides an adequate return is no easy task.\r\n\r\nThis is where our experienced team at UCAS comes in to assist our municipal clients with professional investment advice.  When it comes to investing public dollars, we focus on safety, liquidity and return, in that order.  Our core business is assisting our clients in developing short-term structured portfolios for their bond proceeds and operating funds. Our goal is to assist our clients in safely generating additional interest earnings for their budgets.\r\n\r\nUCAS is a federally registered investment advisor. For more information about our qualifications and business practices please see the following <a href="/our-library/pdf/Umbaugh_Brochure-Form_ADV_Part_2-120111.pdf" target="_blank"><strong>brochure</strong></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>We provide the following <a href="http://cashadvisory.umbaugh.com/services" >services</a>:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Bond Proceeds Investment Advisory</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Operating Funds Investment Advisory</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Banking Request for Proposal Services</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Construction Fund Administration Services</strong></li>\r\n</ul>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4-revision-11', '', '', '2012-03-06 15:52:53', '2012-03-06 15:52:53', '', 4, 'http://cashadvisory.umbaugh.com/4-revision-11', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
